Set Shell "zsh"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Output whoami4.gif

Hide
Type "claude --bare --dangerously-skip-permissions --mcp-config ./site/demos/mcp-demo.json --system-prompt 'You are demonstrating the bray MCP server. Never mention the users name or any personal information. Be concise. Use only nostr-bray MCP tools.'"
Enter
Sleep 10s
Show
Type "Use the whoami tool to check which identity is active"
Enter
Sleep 20s
Ctrl+C
Sleep 2s
